      by simpa using hI, by simp‚ü©)
    (fun I hI ‚Ü¶ ‚ü®I.asIdeal.toAddSubgroup,
      ‚ü®hI, I.mul_mem_left, fun r x hx ‚Ü¶ I.mul_mem_right x (r.unop) hx‚ü©, subset_rfl‚ü©)

